software: Photo: The Oregonian..Disciples garland Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh's Rolls-Royce with flowers during the daily driveby, a ritual at the commune. He occassionally stopped to speak with disciples or hand out gifts..Amassing a fleet of 74 luxury cars, makes perfect sense to the disciples of Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh, the Indian mystic who takes daily drives around the 64,229-acre Oregon ranch bought by his followers in 1981.
